assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Bajaj Finance Ltd. operates as a non-banking financial company in India. It offers durable, lifestyle, digital product, two and three wheeler, retailer, developer, used car, vendor, light engineering, corporate, and warehouse finance; personal, gold, home, business, working capital, and professional loans; and loan against fixed deposits, shares, properties, and securities. The company provides extended warranty; retail EMI; e-commerce; lease rental discounting; EMI cards, and co-branded credit cards and wallets, as well as offers investment services, such as fixed deposits and mutual funds. The company was formerly known as Bajaj Auto Finance Limited and changed its name to Bajaj Finance Limited in September 2010. The company was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Pune, India. Bajaj Finance Ltd. is a subsidiary of Bajaj Finserv Limited.
